Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
Under instructions from the RTA, CBRE is pleased to offer 7 Sirius Road, Lane Cove for sale by expressions of interest.

7 Sirius Road is located in the heart of the Lane Cove Industrial precinct.  This freestanding building is close to Epping Rd and to existing occupiers such as Fitness First, Optus ad Cochlear.

Internally 7 Sirius Rd represents a true 'vanilla' industrial building.  Both lower levels offer high clearance warehouse space accessed via separate roller shutter doors.  The upper level offers a small portion of office space whilst the rooftop provides 38 car spaces.

We strongly encourage you to consider this existing industrial opportunity.  Further details are available from the appointed agents and expressions of interest closes 9th July 2009 at 12pm.

* Warehouse space with great access.
* Ample parking on site.
* High Clearance warehouse.
* Large hardstand area for exclusive use.
* Ideal for those needing additional storage space.
* Contact CBRE now for an immediate inspection.

CBRE are delighted to present the Lower North Shore’s newest premium industrial estate, Arc Lane Cove, proudly developed by Hannas. The estate offers 51 self-storage units from 20sqm to 75sqm and 48 modern, warehouse units with flexible mezzanine office space from 95sqm to 301sqm for sale. Occupiers for this property will enjoy fast access to Sydney CBD, Chatswood, Macquarie Park as well as all other areas of Sydney via the M2. Arc Lane Cove features include;

-Secure complex with 24/7 access
-20ft container access
-5.8m to 6.3m internal clearance
-3 phase power
-Modern mezzanine workspaces
-IN2 light industrial zoning
